{"type":"message","id":"6aa9ca7c","parentId":"831ba4f3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:40:01.273Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue clearly. The `run_live_daily_v1.sh` script uses `account_holdings_*.csv` as the holdings file. This is the file that comes from the THS (同花顺) exports - the real account data. It has 45 holdings.\n\nBut 张玲 is saying she only has 25 stocks. This suggests that:\n1. Either the THS export is including holdings from multiple accounts (or including historical holdings that have been sold)\n2. Or 张玲 is counting only her \"main\" paper portfolio (25 stocks) and not the other sleeves\n\nLooking at the paper portfolio files:\n- `paper_defensive_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - 2 stocks (from panel)\n\n\n- `paper_balanced_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - 3 stocks\n- `paper_aggressive_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - 0 stocks\n- `paper_exit_dual_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - 3 stocks\n- `paper_exit_tight_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - 1 stock\n- `paper_alpha55_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - 0 stocks\n\nThese are all the separate sleeves within the paper trading system, each with their own set of holdings.\n\nI'm realizing the core issue: 张玲 only recognizes 25 stocks as her actual portfolio, but the system is pulling holdings from all 8 of these sleeves and combining them, which inflates the count to 45. The daily execution card is aggregating across every sleeve instead of just showing her core holdings. The 20 extra stocks are likely distributed across these various paper trading sleeves, so 张玲 probably wants me to focus on the main 25-stock portfolio instead of the aggregated view.","thinkingSignature":"f04f6f09bfb01be3bcc74a5b9188b24d6fc07874417cc21a645693bc8c45ef7c"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了。\n\n**实际情况：**\n- `account_holdings_20260330.csv`（同花顺导出）：**45 只**（40 A股 + 4 港股 + 1 ETF）\n- `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv`（模拟盘组合）：**25 只**（张玲认可的组合）\n\n**问题根源：** 每日执行卡脚本 `run_live_daily_v1.sh` 读取的是同花顺导出的 `account_holdings_*.csv`（真实账户持仓），其中混入了其他不在张玲主组合里的持仓（比如各个 paper sleeve 的票，以及可能已经清仓但未同步的票）。\n\n张玲实际认可的持仓应以 `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` 为准。\n\n---\n\n有两个修复方向：\n\n1. **快速修复**：让舆情监控用的每日执行卡改读 `paper_portfolio_positions_latest_csv`（25只）\n2. **彻底排查**：梳理 45 只里哪 20 只是多余，来源是哪个 sleeve/账户\n\n先走快速修复，还是先把45只的来源拆清楚？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":31070,"output":589,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56752,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774856384114,"responseId":"06195bc0868291866a96cf8e18a274a3"}}
