{"type":"message","id":"55375ecb","parentId":"368bfab4","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:44:49.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand. The `norm_h` function sets `currency` from the data. For `account_holdings_20260330.csv`, the currency column is:\n- CNY for A-shares and ETF\n- HKD for HK stocks\n\nSo when it filters:\n- `a_stock = [h for h in holdings if h[\"currency\"] != \"HKD\"]` = 40 (all CNY entries = 40 A-shares + 1 ETF)\n- `hk_stock = [h for h in holdings if h[\"currency\"] == \"HKD\"]` = 4\n\n\n- `etf_stock = [h for h in holdings if h[\"asset_type\"] == \"etf\" or h[\"symbol\"].startswith(\"5\") or \"ETF\" in h.get(\"name\",\"\").upper()]` = 1\n\nThe display logic adds the ETF to the A-share count since it's not filtered out by the HKD check, so it shows 40 + 1 = 41 A-shares, but the user is seeing 45 in the screenshot.\n\nLooking at the actual file data, there are 40 A-shares, 4 HK stocks, and 1 ETF totaling 45 entries, which matches what the user is seeing. The paper portfolio only has 25 entries, so the 45 count is coming from the account holdings file. The real question is why the card at 15:35 is reading from the account holdings data when it should be using the paper portfolio.\n\nThe card is labeled as \"模拟盘模式\" but reading from real account holdings—that's the bug. The fix needs to happen in `generate_daily_exec_card.py` by having it read from the paper portfolio positions file instead of the account holdings file. The paper portfolio CSV has the correct 25 entries with the proper columns like quantity and cost basis.","thinkingSignature":"2a2ab707cf79ef66567efb9a6723ef416319866ff9587af12d40ec93b1a02bbe"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题根源了。\n\n**问题确认：**\n- `generate_daily_exec_card.py` 读取的是 `account_holdings_20260330.csv`（同花顺导出），里面有 45 条记录\n- 筛选逻辑：`currency != \"HKD\"` 即视为 A 股，把 ETF 也算进去了\n- 实际纸面组合只有 25 只\n\n我来修复这个脚本，让它读取 `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv`（25只），而不是 `account_holdings`。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vx40ci9gys51_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":80,"limit":80,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_exec_card.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51293,"output":552,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76938,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774856675707,"responseId":"06195ce3f483adf855c2aeafd40d37c0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"49413195","parentId":"55375ecb","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:44:49.479Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vx40ci9gys51_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    \"300622.SZ\": \"博士眼镜\", \"300660.SZ\": \"江苏雷利\", \"300710.SZ\": \"精进电动\",\n    \"300777.SZ\": \"中简科技\", \"300829.SZ\": \"金丹科技\", \"300932.SZ\": \"三友联众\",\n    \"301101.SZ\": \"明月镜片\", \"301333.SZ\": \"长光华芯\", \"301591.SZ\": \"四川黄金\",\n    \"511880.SH\": \"银华日利\", \"600159.SH\": \"大龙地产\", \"600363.SH\": \"联创光电\",\n    \"600493.SH\": \"凤竹纺织\", \"600593.SH\": \"大连圣亚\", \"600805.SH\": \"江苏金智\",\n    \"603629.SH\": \"利通电子\", \"688543.SH\": \"纳睿雷达\", \"688567.SH\": \"金山办公\",\n}\n\ndef get_holdings():\n    # 优先从同花顺真实持仓文件读取（避免旧模拟仓数据残留）\n    # 格式：ths_app_holdings_YYYYMMDD.csv\n    f = get_latest_by_date(\"ths_app_holdings_????????.csv\", QUANT)\n    if f:\n        rows = []\n        with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n            for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n                sym = r.get(\"symbol\", \"\")\n                qty = r.get(\"quantity\", \"\").strip()\n                if sym and qty and qty != \"0\":\n                    # 补充 name（THS 文件 name 列为空）和 currency\n                    r[\"name\"] = THS_NAME_MAP.get(sym, sym)\n                    if sym.endswith(\".HK\"):\n                        r[\"currency\"] = \"HKD\"\n                    else:\n                        r[\"currency\"] = \"CNY\"\n                    rows.append(r)\n        if rows:\n            return rows\n    # 回退：手动维护的 account_holdings_YYYYMMDD.csv\n    f = get_latest_by_date(\"account_holdings_????????.csv\", QUANT)\n    if not f:\n        return []\n    rows = []\n    with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n        for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n            rows.append(r)\n    return rows\n\ndef get_intelligence_brief():\n    f = REPORTS / \"intelligence_brief_latest.md\"\n    return load_txt(f) if f.exists() else \"\"\n\n# ====== 解析策略报告 ======\ndef parse_strategy(content):\n    result = {\n        \"buy_count\": 0, \"sell_count\": 0,\n        \"buy_candidates\": [],\n        \"risk_off\": None,\n        \"market_breadth\": None,\n        \"report_date\": None,\n    }\n    if not content:\n        return result\n\n    m = re.search(r\"形成 `(\\d+)` 个去重 BUY 候选\", content)\n    if m: result[\"buy_count\"] = int(m.group(1))\n    m = re.search(r\"形成 `(\\d+)` 个去重 SELL 候选\", content)\n    if m: result[\"sell_count\"] = int(m.group(1))\n    m = re.search(r\"宽度门禁：当前 `([\\d.]+)%`\", content)\n    if m: result[\"market_breadth\"] = float(m.group(1))\n\n    # 从表格提取候选（含价格）\n    for m in re.finditer(\n        r\"^\\|\\s*(\\d+)\\s*\\|\\s*(\\d{6}\\.[A-Z]{2})\\s*\\|\\s*([^|]+?)\\s*\\|\\s*[\\d.]+\\s*\\|\\s*\\w+\\s*\\|\\s*([\\d.]+)\\s*\\|\\s*(买入|卖出|观望)\\s*\\|\",\n        content, re.MULTILINE\n    ):\n        rank, code, name, price, action = m.group(1), m.group(2), m.group(3).strip(), m.group(4), m.group(5)\n        result[\"buy_candidates\"].append({\n            \"rank\": rank, \"code\": code, \"name\": clean(name),\n            \"price\": price, \"action\": action,\n            \"stop_loss\": \"\", \"take_profit\": \"\", \"trigger\": \"\"\n        })\n\n    # 尝试找止损/止盈（从 BUY 候选行的后面部分）\n    for cand in result[\"buy_candidates\"]:\n        code = cand[\"code\"]\n        # 在内容中搜索该代码相关的止损止盈\n        pattern = re.compile(\n            rf\"`{re.escape(code)}`[^\\n]*\\n.*?止损[/:：]\\s*([\\d.]+).*?止[盈盈率][/:：]\\s*([\\d.]+)\",\n            re.DOTALL\n\n[216 more lines in file. Use offset=160 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774856689459}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5d80160","parentId":"49413195","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:44:56.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the `get_holdings()` function. It reads from:\n1. `ths_app_holdings_*.csv` (THS app holdings)\n2. Falls back to `account_holdings_*.csv`\n\nThe issue is that these files have 45 entries (including all paper sleeves and other accounts), not 25.\n\nThe fix should be to read from `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` instead. But that file has a different format:\n- `symbol, asset_type, name, quantity, cost_price`\n\nWhile `account_holdings_*.csv` has:\n- `ts_code, qty, name, cost_price, currency, asset_type`\n  \nI need to check what the `norm_h` function actually expects and how it maps fields between these two formats.","thinkingSignature":"20ccfc210c5fea95c6d9414e508a34c9d4e5d87d0f4c75d246f7e633c8db036d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4z8omzt6kmka_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":196,"limit":20,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_exec_card.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52899,"output":228,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774856689479,"responseId":"06195cf15435b7942ec19bf7a7b9303b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"150e3c4b","parentId":"a5d80160","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:44:56.693Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4z8omzt6kmka_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def norm_h(h):\n    return {\n        \"symbol\": h.get(\"ts_code\") or h.get(\"symbol\", \"\"),\n        \"name\": h.get(\"name\", \"\"),\n        \"quantity\": int(h.get(\"qty\") or h.get(\"quantity\") or 0),\n        \"asset_type\": h.get(\"asset_type\", \"stock\"),\n        \"currency\": h.get(\"currency\", \"CNY\"),\n        \"cost_price\": float(h.get(\"cost_price\") or 0),\n    }\n\n# ====== 构建执行卡 ======\ndef build_exec_card(strategy, audit, holdings, ibrief):\n    now = datetime.now()\n    date_str = now.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    holdings = [norm_h(h) for h in holdings]\n\n    lines = []\n    lines.append(\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\")\n    lines.append(f\"📋 每日执行卡 v2\")\n    lines.append(f\"{date_str} {now.strftime('%H:%M')} | 交易日\")\n\n[160 more lines in file. Use offset=216 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774856696677}}
{"type":"message","id":"260cbedc","parentId":"150e3c4b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:45:09.079Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `norm_h` function normalizes both formats:\n- `ts_code` → `symbol` (for account_holdings)\n- `symbol` → `symbol` (for ths_app_holdings and paper_portfolio)\n- `qty` → `quantity` (for account_holdings)\n- `quantity` → `quantity` (for others)\n- `cost_price` → `cost_price`\n- `asset_type` → `asset_type`\n- `currency` → `currency`\n\nThe `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` format is:\n```\nsymbol,asset_type,name,quantity,cost_price\n\n\n```\n\nIt doesn't have `currency` or `ts_code`. So `norm_h` would set `symbol` from `symbol`, keep `asset_type` as-is, use `quantity` and `cost_price` directly, but `currency` defaults to \"CNY\" and `ts_code` would be empty. The issue is that HK stocks won't be properly flagged since there's no `.HK` suffix or currency information to distinguish them.\n\nLooking at the actual CSV data, the HK stocks are marked with `.HK` suffixes like `06969.HK`, `09988.HK`, `00700.HK`, and `02611.HK`, while A-shares use `.SH` or `.SZ`. The paper portfolio format doesn't have a currency column, so I need to infer it from the symbol suffix instead.\n\n```\nFor the `get_holdings` function, I should read directly from `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` rather than aggregating across multiple account files. The card is meant to display the paper portfolio composition, not the consolidated holdings across different accounts.\n```\n\nLet me create a more robust approach that parses the CSV format correctly and infers currency from the symbol suffix to properly categorize HK stocks versus A-shares.","thinkingSignature":"8500c2e8f913796745e66bd98baec2f0bed166b7d0cf4c1849a8505b515c9b5d"},{"type":"text","text":"问题清楚了：`get_holdings()` 读取的是 `account_holdings_*.csv`（45条），但应该读 `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv`（25条）。\n\n修复方案：改 `get_holdings()` 优先从纸面组合持仓文件读取。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yvkhbmbs0h3e_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":1,"limit":90,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_exec_card.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53358,"output":500,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774856696693,"responseId":"06195cf89601ba50917bbd5daaa67607"}}
{"type":"message","id":"946d706f","parentId":"260cbedc","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:45:09.166Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yvkhbmbs0h3e_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n每日执行卡生成器 v2\n增强版：① 个股目标价/止损价 ② 持仓盈亏分析 ③ 舆情摘要\n\"\"\"\n\nimport re, json, csv, sys, html as html_mod\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw/workspace\"\nREPORTS = WORKSPACE / \"research/reports\"\nQUANT = Path.home() / \".openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports\"\nFEISHU_WEBHOOK = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/f54d31a7-226d-4fac-aeaf-44b84c5c85b7\"\n\n\ndef is_trading_day() -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断今天是否为 A 股交易日（周一~周五）。\"\"\"\n    return datetime.now().weekday() < 5\n\n\ndef clean(text):\n    text = re.sub(r\"<[^>]+>\", \"\", str(text or \"\"))\n    return html_mod.unescape(text).strip()\n\ndef load_json(path):\n    try:\n        return json.loads(Path(path).read_text())\n    except:\n        return {}\n\ndef load_txt(path):\n    try:\n        return Path(path).read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    except:\n        return \"\"\n\ndef get_latest_file(pattern, base):\n    files = sorted(Path(base).glob(pattern), key=lambda p: p.stat().st_mtime, reverse=True)\n    return files[0] if files else None\n\ndef get_latest_by_date(pattern, base):\n    \"\"\"按文件名日期（YYYYMMDD）选取最新，不依赖 mtime。\"\"\"\n    files = list(Path(base).glob(pattern))\n    if not files:\n        return None\n    # 提取日期后缀，日期格式为 8 位数字\n    dated = []\n    for f in files:\n        m = re.search(r\"(\\d{8})\", f.name)\n        if m:\n            dated.append((m.group(1), f))\n    if not dated:\n        return None\n    dated.sort(key=lambda x: x[0], reverse=True)\n    return dated[0][1]\n\n# ====== 数据获取 ======\ndef get_strategy_report():\n    f = get_latest_file(\"today_stock_strategy_report_????????.md\", QUANT)\n    if not f:\n        f = QUANT / \"today_stock_strategy_report_latest.md\"\n    return load_txt(f) if f.exists() else \"\"\n\ndef get_audit():\n    f = get_latest_file(\"daily_strategy_audit_*.json\", QUANT)\n    return load_json(f) if f else {}\n\n# ths_app_holdings 的 name 列为空，补充名称映射\nTHS_NAME_MAP = {\n    \"000930.SZ\": \"中粮科技\", \"001336.SZ\": \"舍得酒业\", \"002188.SZ\": \"新开普\",\n    \"002316.SZ\": \"键桥通讯\", \"002494.SZ\": \"华斯股份\", \"002715.SZ\": \"新澳股份\",\n    \"002719.SZ\": \"麦趣尔\", \"002780.SZ\": \"三棵树\", \"002802.SZ\": \"洪汇新材\",\n    \"002817.SZ\": \"博观\", \"002820.SZ\": \"凯莱英\", \"002827.SZ\": \"百奥泰\",\n    \"002830.SZ\": \"名雕股份\", \"002883.SZ\": \"中设股份\", \"002888.SZ\": \"惠达卫浴\",\n    \"002920.SZ\": \"瑞玛精密\", \"002963.SZ\": \"银都股份\", \"003003.SZ\": \"蓝天燃气\",\n    \"003030.SZ\": \"英特集团\", \"00700.HK\": \"腾讯控股\", \"02611.HK\": \"汇丰控股\",\n    \"06969.HK\": \"中教控股\", \"09988.HK\": \"阿里巴巴\", \"300030.SZ\": \"阳普医疗\",\n    \"300200.SZ\": \"高新兴\", \"300464.SZ\": \"星徽股份\", \"300500.SZ\": \"启迪设计\",\n    \"300622.SZ\": \"博士眼镜\", \"300660.SZ\": \"江苏雷利\", \"300710.SZ\": \"精进电动\",\n    \"300777.SZ\": \"中简科技\", \"300829.SZ\": \"金丹科技\", \"300932.SZ\": \"三友联众\",\n    \"301101.SZ\": \"明月镜片\", \"301333.SZ\": \"长光华芯\", \"301591.SZ\": \"四川黄金\",\n    \"511880.SH\": \"银华日利\", \"600159.SH\": \"大龙地产\", \"600363.SH\": \"联创光电\",\n    \"600493.SH\": \"凤竹纺织\", \"600593.SH\": \"大连圣亚\", \"600805.SH\": \"江苏金智\",\n    \"603629.SH\": \"利通电子\", \"688543.SH\": \"纳睿雷达\", \"688567.SH\": \"金山办公\",\n}\n\ndef get_holdings():\n    # 优先从同花顺真实持仓文件读取（避免旧模拟仓数据残留）\n    # 格式：ths_app_holdings_YYYYMMDD.csv\n\n[285 more lines in file. Use offset=91 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774856709150}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0497c34","parentId":"946d706f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:45:36.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture. The `get_holdings()` function reads from:\n1. `ths_app_holdings_*.csv` (THS app holdings)\n2. Falls back to `account_holdings_*.csv`\n\nBoth have 45 entries. The paper portfolio CSV has 25 entries. The fix should be to read from `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` instead.\n\nHere's my fix plan:\n1. Add a new function `get_paper_portfolio_holdings()` that reads from `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv`\n2. Modify `get_holdings()` to prioritize this new data source\n\n\n3. I need to examine the paper portfolio CSV format more carefully—it uses `symbol` instead of `ts_code`, doesn't have a `currency` column, and has `quantity` as the field name. Since HK stocks are already marked with `.HK` suffixes in the data, I can detect them the same way the THS files do.\n\nLooking at the actual paper portfolio file, I see it only contains 3 HK stocks (`06969.HK`, `09988.HK`, `00700.HK`) with `asset_type=h`, while the account holdings file has 4 HK stocks including `02611.HK`. The paper portfolio has 25 total entries but the account holdings shows 45 with duplicates and extra holdings.\n\nThe real issue is that the card should display the paper portfolio (25 stocks) rather than the account holdings (45 stocks). I need to modify `get_holdings()` to read from `paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` as the primary source, falling back to the account holdings file only if needed.\n\nSince the paper portfolio format doesn't explicitly identify ETFs, I'll need to add ETF detection logic based on symbols starting with \"5\" or fund-related naming conventions. I should also make sure HK stocks are properly flagged by checking for `.HK` in the symbol or `asset_type=h`.\n\nNow I'm writing the fix that handles these edge cases.","thinkingSignature":"c6a42166034ed248302fa64ba09ed289ded1d426eb0bf0c39d61d5a2e55f7f22"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lcj504nrojwp_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_exec_card.py","old_string":"def get_holdings():\n    # 优先从同花顺真实持仓文件读取（避免旧模拟仓数据残留）\n    # 格式：ths_app_holdings_YYYYMMDD.csv\n    f = get_latest_by_date(\"ths_app_holdings_????????.csv\", QUANT)\n    if f:\n        rows = []\n        with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n            for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n                sym = r.get(\"symbol\", \"\")\n                qty = r.get(\"quantity\", \"\").strip()\n                if sym and qty and qty != \"0\":\n                    # 补充 name（THS 文件 name 列为空）和 currency\n                    r[\"name\"] = THS_NAME_MAP.get(sym, sym)\n                    if sym.endswith(\".HK\"):\n                        r[\"currency\"] = \"HKD\"\n                    else:\n                        r[\"currency\"] = \"CNY\"\n                    rows.append(r)\n        if rows:\n            return rows\n    # 回退：手动维护的 account_holdings_YYYYMMDD.csv\n    f = get_latest_by_date(\"account_holdings_????????.csv\", QUANT)\n    if not f:\n        return []\n    rows = []\n    with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n        for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n            rows.append(r)\n    return rows","new_string":"def _infer_currency_and_asset_type(symbol, asset_type):\n    \"\"\"从 symbol 后缀推断 currency 和归一化 asset_type。\"\"\"\n    if symbol.endswith(\".HK\"):\n        return \"HKD\", \"stock\"\n    at = str(asset_type or \"\").lower()\n    if at in (\"fund\", \"etf\"):\n        return \"CNY\", \"etf\"\n    if symbol.startswith(\"5\") or symbol.startswith(\"1\") or \"ETF\" in symbol.upper():\n        return \"CNY\", \"etf\"\n    return \"CNY\", \"stock\"\n\n\ndef get_holdings():\n    # 优先从纸面组合持仓读取（正确的模拟盘口径，25只）\n    # 格式：paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv\n    f = QUANT / \"paper_portfolio_positions_latest.csv\"\n    if f.exists():\n        rows = []\n        with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n            for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n                sym = r.get(\"symbol\", \"\").strip()\n                qty = r.get(\"quantity\", \"\").strip()\n                if sym and qty and qty != \"0\":\n                    r[\"currency\"], r[\"asset_type\"] = _infer_currency_and_asset_type(\n                        sym, r.get(\"asset_type\", \"\")\n                    )\n                    rows.append(r)\n        if rows:\n            return rows\n\n    # 回退①：ths_app_holdings（同花顺 App 导出）\n    f = get_latest_by_date(\"ths_app_holdings_????????.csv\", QUANT)\n    if f:\n        rows = []\n        with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n            for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n                sym = r.get(\"symbol\", \"\")\n                qty = r.get(\"quantity\", \"\").strip()\n                if sym and qty and qty != \"0\":\n                    r[\"name\"] = THS_NAME_MAP.get(sym, sym)\n                    if sym.endswith(\".HK\"):\n                        r[\"currency\"] = \"HKD\"\n                    else:\n                        r[\"currency\"] = \"CNY\"\n                    rows.append(r)\n        if rows:\n            return rows\n\n    # 回退②：account_holdings（手动维护）\n    f = get_latest_by_date(\"account_holdings_????????.csv\", QUANT)\n    if not f:\n        return []\n    rows = []\n    with open(f, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\") as fp:\n        for r in csv.DictReader(fp):\n            rows.append(r)\n    return rows"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55011,"output":1302,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81406,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774856709166,"responseId":"06195d0501ce4087092b0a7fe6d3c26a"}}
