{"type":"message","id":"bbe1c9cf","parentId":"2566844d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:46:33.723Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the issue clearly. In the paper portfolio:\n- 588000.SH has `asset_type=stock` but it's actually an index fund (ETF)\n- My `_infer_currency_and_asset_type` function was overriding it to ETF because the symbol starts with \"5\"\n\nThe actual correct breakdown is:\n- 22 A股 (asset_type=stock, not starting with 5, not HK)\n- 2 港股 (asset_type=hk)\n- 1 ETF (588000.SH, starts with 5)\n\nTotal = 25只\n\nBut my script is showing:\n\n\n- A股 23只 (22 stock + 588000.SH which got overridden to ETF but still counted as A股 because currency=CNY)\n- 港股 2只\n- ETF 1只 (588000.SH)\n\nThe problem is that 588000.SH is being counted twice—once as an A股 and once as an ETF—because my override logic is incorrectly applying the \"5\" prefix rule to reclassify it as an ETF even though it already has the correct asset_type in the source data.\n\nI need to fix `_infer_currency_and_asset_type` to respect the original asset_type when it's already explicitly set to something other than \"stock\", rather than overriding everything based on the symbol prefix. So the real problem is that I'm inferring ETF status from the symbol prefix when the source data already has a correct asset_type field - I should trust that instead of overriding it based on whether it starts with \"5\".","thinkingSignature":"232b15f27ca426cbb38a761a0f6b5850d09cc00a2fbc2be4cbf63c7c635fe0f7"},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题：588000.SH（华安日利货币）在纸面组合里 `asset_type=stock`，但我的代码按前缀 \"5\" 把它归为 ETF，导致重复计算（A 股 23 + ETF 1 里都包含了它，实际只有 22 只 A 股 + 2 港股 + 1 ETF = 25 只）。\n\n修正分类逻辑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5qjvurr1ziyo_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"old_string":"def _infer_currency_and_asset_type(symbol, asset_type):\n    \"\"\"从 symbol 后缀推断 currency 和归一化 asset_type。\"\"\"\n    if symbol.endswith(\".HK\"):\n        return \"HKD\", \"stock\"\n    at = str(asset_type or \"\").lower()\n    if at in (\"fund\", \"etf\"):\n        return \"CNY\", \"etf\"\n    if symbol.startswith(\"5\") or symbol.startswith(\"1\") or \"ETF\" in symbol.upper():\n        return \"CNY\", \"etf\"\n    return \"CNY\", \"stock\"","new_string":"def _infer_currency_and_asset_type(symbol, asset_type):\n    \"\"\"从 symbol 后缀推断 currency；asset_type 以原始数据为准（588000 等基金代码已在 CSV 中标为 stock）。\"\"\"\n    if symbol.endswith(\".HK\"):\n        return \"HKD\", \"stock\"\n    return \"CNY\", str(asset_type or \"stock\")"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":59493,"output":608,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85194,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774856775782,"responseId":"06195d47625cc92313e1c4207909136a"}}
