{"type":"message","id":"8f9c4b35","parentId":"1b8bcd5f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T07:47:44.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling says to remove duplicates and check again. She's referring to the 45-stock holdings file `account_holdings_20260330.csv`. Let me check that file for duplicates.","thinkingSignature":"913c291d59f318afd7957ad5e2a4426c039251db6b488a3c50a416783dbaaf73"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，我来看一下 45 只的去重情况。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4ds4nqntqv6o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport csv\nfrom collections import Counter\n\nwith open('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/account_holdings_20260330.csv') as f:\n    rows = list(csv.DictReader(f))\n\nprint(f'总行数（含标题）: {len(rows)+1}')\nprint(f'总记录数: {len(rows)}')\n\n# 按 symbol 去重\nsyms = [r['ts_code'] for r in rows]\ndupes = {s:c for s,c in Counter(syms).items() if c>1}\nprint(f'去重后: {len(set(syms))}')\nprint(f'重复 symbol: {dupes}')\n\n# 按 name 去重\nnames = [r['name'] for r in rows]\nname_dupes = {s:c for s,c in Counter(names).items() if c>1}\nprint(f'名称重复: {name_dupes}')\n\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":287,"cacheRead":25093,"cacheWrite":55585,"totalTokens":81039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774856853013,"responseId":"06195d95dde541a4435374bfbfa751cc"}}
